## 📋 标准来源

### 核心标准

- **[Clean Code](https://www.oreilly.com/library/view/clean-code-a/9780136083238/)** - 代码整洁之道
- **[The Pragmatic Programmer](https://pragprog.com/titles/tpp20/the-pragmatic-programmer-20th-anniversary-edition/)** - 程序员修炼之道
- **[Google Style Guides](https://google.github.io/styleguide/)** - Google 代码风格指南
- **[Microsoft Coding Conventions](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/visualstudio/ide/coding-conventions)** - Microsoft 编码约定

### 行业最佳实践

- **SOLID Principles** - SOLID 原则
- **DRY (Don't Repeat Yourself)** - 不要重复自己
- **KISS (Keep It Simple, Stupid)** - 保持简单
- **YAGNI (You Aren't Gonna Need It)** - 你不会需要它

