## 📝 命名规范

### 变量命名

```python
# ✅ 好的命名
user_name = "John"
total_price = 100.00
is_active = True
max_retry_count = 3

# ❌ 坏的命名
name = "John"  # 缺少上下文
tp = 100.00  # 难以理解
flag = True  # 含义不明
n = 3  # 无意义
```

### 函数命名

```python
# ✅ 好的命名
def calculate_total_price(items):
    ...

def validate_user_email(email):
    ...

def get_user_by_id(user_id):
    ...

# ❌ 坏的命名
def calc(items):
    ...

def check(email):
    ...

def get(id):
    ...
```

### 类命名

```python
# ✅ 好的命名
class UserService:
    ...

class PaymentProcessor:
    ...

class DatabaseConnection:
    ...

# ❌ 坏的命名
class Service:
    ...

class Processor:
    ...

class Manager:
    ...
```

